                     <interp inst="t18370227-713-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370227-cd-14" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370227-713-offence-1 t18370227-cd-14"></join>17th of february</rs>, 181bs. weight of fat, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370227-name-249" type="victimName">
